doctor_utters: How may I help you today?
Do you have shortness of breath?
Do you have chest pain or tightness?
Does the chest pain get worse when you take a deep breath or cough?
Does the chest pain radiate to your arms, neck, or jaw?
Do you have a history of heart disease or high blood pressure?
Have you been exposed to any environmental irritants such as smoke or dust?
Have you been in contact with people with similar symptoms in the past 2 weeks?
